1. Khai bao bien config database trong file .env
    DB_HOST=localhost
    DB_PORT=3307
    DB_USER=root
    DB_PASS=123456
    DB_NAME=hoidanit

2. Khai bao template trong file .env.example
    DB_HOST=
    DB_PORT=
    DB_USER=
    DB_PASS=
    DB_NAME=

3. Chuyen code connect db vao file /config/database.js
    - bat buoc phai require dotenv neu muon dung
        require('dotenv').config();
    - Nho export module de co the goi trong server.js
        